{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d4c2720bb2","title":"在黄炎培关于提倡平地深葬的来信上的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"b2e9f1f0cf","index":0,"year":1958,"month":1,"day":null,"articleId":"d4c2720bb2"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji38","name":"毛泽东全集第38卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/38-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji38":{"comments":[{"id":"3f4665b90d","publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"d4c2720bb2","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"黄炎培，当时任中国民主建国会主任委员、全国人大常委会副委员长。"},{"id":"4bdc4f41bc","publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"d4c2720bb2","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指黄炎培1958年1月29日给毛泽东的信。信中说：我最近写了一篇《试信平地深葬》文，认为一般采用土葬法，把很好的可耕地为理葬死人而浪费，这种不合理的风俗习惯，应按农业发展纲要修正草案第二十三条的规定，予以改变。此文曾发表在1月11日《人民日报》和1月12日《新闻日报》，是一种公开建议性质。各报先后转载，人民来信有直接给我的，有送报纸发表的，纷纷表示赞成。我以为此时应广泛地宣传，请新华社宣传一下。"}],"contents":[{"id":"86aa2cdfa7","type":"title","text":"在黄炎培以关于提倡平地深葬的来信上的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"d4c2720bb2"},{"id":"3f4665b90d","type":"paragraph","text":"电话告黄：信收收到了，谢谢他。我赞成他的意见。因忙不写回信了。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"d4c2720bb2"}],"page":{"id":"78d4aa4400","publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"d4c2720bb2","start":509,"end":509}}}},"__N_SSG":true}